/* ============================================================================
   47. Final Best Practices and Optimization
============================================================================ */

/*
   - Use custom utility classes for cleaner and reusable styles.
   - Use `rem` and `em` for consistent font sizing and scaling.
   - Avoid fixed pixel values for responsive design, use percentages, `vw`, or `vh`.
   - Optimize animations and transitions for performance.
   - Follow accessibility best practices such as ensuring keyboard navigation, color contrast, and appropriate use of ARIA attributes.
   - Keep your CSS modular by breaking it into smaller, reusable components.
*/

